				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">1.  Are there any doccumented performance issues on file for your spouse?
<br />
2.  How long has your spouse been employed there?
<br />
3.  Did she have signing authority on writing chacks to purchase items on behalf of the company and was part of her implied or stated responsibilities the reconcilation of any bank accounts that were drawn off of by her on behalf of the company?
<br />

<br />
The best bet is to speak to your state's dept. of labor, I will tell you this though if you answer yes to 1 or 3 it is very likely you will end up with nothing or end up in court.
<br />

<br />
