				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It is against the law for them to withold any money she earned. They have to pay her regardless of whether she is guilty or not. That includes any unsed vacation pay and sick pay if it is payed out when employement ends.
<br />

<br />
Get a lawyer, have the lawyer handle everything and don't make any statements until you do.
<br />

